A Friendly reminder to Cardinal Fans.
The Foundation of Sportsmanship in the stands

1. Do your best to understand the rules of the game.

2. Represent Boone Central- Our Kids. Our Coaches- In a positive manner

3. Recognize the Great and Support the Struggle

4. Exhibit respect to the Officials. Even on bad calls.

5. Always respect the Opponent. Even Rivals.

6. Be Prideful. Be a Supporter. Be
Great.

10 up or 10 down always stay together.
Together on 3.. 1. 2. 3....

#gocards
